WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: uz

00:00:00.430 --> 00:00:04.540
Ovoz fokusi mavjud bo‘lgandan so‘ng, audio fokus
holatining o‘zgarishi haqida tashvishlanishimiz kerak.

00:00:04.540 --> 00:00:09.030
Shunday qilib, ushbu hujjatda 
"AudioManager.OnAudioFocusChangeListener" uchun, 

00:00:09.030 --> 00:00:12.960
biz yangi "onAudioFocusChange" 
usulini amalga oshirishimiz kerakligi aytilmoqda,

00:00:12.960 --> 00:00:15.652
shuningdek, bu yerda biz yangi audio fokus 
holatini taqdim etilishini kutamiz.

00:00:15.652 --> 00:00:18.880
Shuningdek, "onAudioFocusChange" 
usulining tavsifida biz ushbu konstantalar bilan 

00:00:18.880 --> 00:00:22.072
ifodalangan to‘rtta mumkin bo‘lgan 
holatlar mavjudligini ko‘rishimiz kerak.

00:00:22.072 --> 00:00:26.821
Bular "AUDIOFOCUS_GAIN" , "AUDIOFOCUS_LOSS" ,
"AUDIOFOCUS_LOSS_TRANSIENT" va

00:00:26.821 --> 00:00:29.700
"AUDIOFOCUS_LOSS_TRANSITION_CAN_DUCK" .

00:00:29.700 --> 00:00:33.800
Shunday qilib, dasturchilar sifatida, 
biz ushbu ilovadagi har bir o‘zgarishlarni 

00:00:33.800 --> 00:00:36.350
ilovamizda ijro etilayotgan media turiga va 
foydalanuvchi nimani kutishiga qarab 

00:00:36.350 --> 00:00:37.610
hal qiluvchi qaror qabul qilishimiz kerak.

00:00:37.610 --> 00:00:40.500
Hozir har bir holat haqida ko‘proq bilish uchun 
ularning har birini ustiga bosishga biroz vaqt ajrating.

00:00:41.540 --> 00:00:44.690
Endi mazkur testda 
ushbu jadvalni to‘ldirishingizni xohlayman.

00:00:44.690 --> 00:00:48.990
Shunday qilib, audio fokus holatlarining har biri 
nimani anglatishini o‘z so‘zlaringiz bilan ta’riflang.

00:00:48.990 --> 00:00:51.765
Ushbu holat o‘zgarganda 
biz "Miwok" ilovamizga kerak deb

00:00:51.765 --> 00:00:54.125
o‘ylagan narsalaringizni yozing.

00:00:54.125 --> 00:00:57.310
Shunday qilib, biz qanday audio ijro etayotganimiz
va ideal foydalanuvchi tajribasi qanday bo‘lishi kerakligi 

00:00:57.310 --> 00:00:59.090
haqida o‘ylashingizni xohlardimn.

